      "name": "Hemolysis index comparison at 2.5 L/min, 2500 RPM",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at the 2.5 L/min and 2500 RPM operating point. Simulation yielded NIH of 0.0031 mg/100 L versus measured 0.0034 mg/100 L. Relative error 8.8%, within the 15% acceptance band."
    },
