      "description": "Simulated pump pressure head compared against experimental measurements at all five COU flow-speed combinations. Mean absolute error 3.2 mmHg across operating points; maximum deviation 5.1 mmHg at 6.0 L/min 4000 RPM. All within the 10 mmHg acceptance criterion."
