    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. CFD model predictions of NIH are within 15% of experimental measurements across all five COU operating points. Worst-case hemolysis condition correctly identified. Relative hemolysis index RH = 0.87 satisfies the RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device. The model is deemed credible for the stated COU.",
